nodes.text: The Adventures of Lanoree Brock, Je'daii Ranger

"The Adventures of Lanoree Brock, Je'daii Ranger" is a short story written by Tim Lebbon that was published on the Kindle Daily Post website on April 24, 2013. The story takes the form of a ship log entry made by Lanoree Brock, set between chapters 2 and 3 of Dawn of the Jedi: Into the Void, and describes her thoughts on her latest mission from the Je'daii Council.
